<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Oscilloscope&amp;action=edit&amp;section=60" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<div class="references-small references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="-moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> Frank Spitzer and Barry Howarth, <i>Principles of modern Instrumentation</i>, Holt, Rinehart and Winston, New York, 1972, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0030802083" class="internal">ISBN 0-03-080208-3</a> pg. 110</li>
